                <DIV class="ReviewHeading">Book Description:</DIV>
                <span id="Label1">fabulous line drawings and 14 Harper&#8217;s Bazar covers, 8 in full color. Ert&eacute;&#8217;s exotic temptresses with tassels, fur muffs, long trains, coifs, more. "Imaginative and colorful...A fascinating glimpse into the development of fashion."&#8212;Arts Review (London).<br></span>
              
